<dl id="n12114h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12114h">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12114h"> 114(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> enter a cloister</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Les sanctions &eacute;taient dures et rigoureuses: <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> d&apos;interminables abstinences de viande et de vin et, dans les cas tr&egrave;s graves, le bannissement temporaire ou l&apos;entr&eacute;e dans un clo&icirc;tre. <br><font color="green">[The sanctions were hard and rigorous: [&hellip;]</font> unceasing abstinence from meat and wine and, in the worst cases, temporary banishment or <mark>entry into a cloister</mark>.] <small> <a name="STCM" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#STCM"><cite title="source">Saint Colomban</cite></a> (1905) 74</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
